divs: Sighting DetailsDriving in Cal. looked up & saw bright light in sky moving east. Told the wife to take picture with cell phone. I knew right away that it was a ufo as I have seen it in AZ. a couple of times. But the wife has never seen one until now.I forgot that she took the picture & when I downloaded it you can clearly see that it is a rectangled, very bright object.It kept flying east & we lost sight of it.
